GENUINE REVIEW: They were both cute especially the sister. They feel like a genuine brother & sister based on how they interact, the sister being a brocon while the little brother is just worried about his older sister. 
Unlike most plots where things escalate quickly where it transitions from one scene to the other, this one is drawn out where it slowly shows the build up until they gave in to desire. The ending with a cliffhanger is also a nice touch, though I wish they would continue the sequel at that moment. The humour was also good with some out of place memes but it had the right balance as to not be a straight up comedy because humour makes or breaks doujins at times. Anyway the story and characters are pretty good, and the censoring wasn't annoying so 10/10 . The sex scenes weren't perfect but the main highlight of this really is the story and characters. If you prefer the plot more than the art then this is the hentai for you. 10/10 SEQUEL PLEASE.
